66
00:05:59,609 --> 00:06:00,693
What breed is it?

67
00:06:00,777 --> 00:06:04,280
It's… Hey, I told you to stay inside.

68
00:06:04,363 --> 00:06:06,866
-Hello, ma'am.
-Hello.

69
00:06:06,949 --> 00:06:09,368
We haven't had breakfast yet.

70
00:06:09,452 --> 00:06:11,412
Take your time. I'll wait.

71
00:06:11,496 --> 00:06:13,956
No. That's not what I mean.

72
00:06:14,457 --> 00:06:15,708
Why don't you join us?

73
00:06:16,459 --> 00:06:17,293
Don't!

74
00:06:31,724 --> 00:06:32,600
I heard

75
