Discharge him.

259
00:19:21,869 --> 00:19:22,870
He says you may take him.

260
00:19:33,297 --> 00:19:34,506
Jae-hyeok.

261
00:19:36,842 --> 00:19:38,302
-Jae-hyeok!
-Yes.

262
00:19:39,303 --> 00:19:40,429
Control the bleeding.

263
00:19:40,512 --> 00:19:41,555
Yes, sir.

264
00:19:49,897 --> 00:19:52,649
This is Emergency Medicine.
We need a brain CT for Kim Ji-hun.

265
00:19:57,237 --> 00:19:59,990
Luckily, there's no nerve damage
or internal bleeding.

266
00:20:01,909 --> 00:20:04,411
Do you want to get the stitches here
or at Plastic Surgery?

267
00:20:04,494 --> 00:20:06,330
You'll have to wait if you want it there.

268
00:20:06,413 --> 00:20:07,873
They're available after 7 p.m.

269
00:20:08,874 --> 00:20:11,376
Is it okay… to get the stitches here?

270
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:13,587
The wound isn't deep, so it would be okay.

271
00:20:15,088 --> 00:20:15,923
Okay.

272
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:18,926
Jae-hyeok, you do it.

273
00:20:19,551 --> 00:20:21,595
-Pardon?
-Set it up, please.

274
00:20:22,846 --> 00:20:23,722
Okay, Dr. Ye.

275
00:20:24,556 --> 00:20:26,016
Come here. Do it with me.

276
00:20:27,184 --> 00:20:29,436
Mr. Kim. You know him, right?

277
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:32,773
He's a good doctor,
so you don't need to worry.

278
00:20:32,856 --> 00:20:34,399
We'll make sure it won't leave a scar.

279
00:20:35,943 --> 00:20:37,653
-Okay.
