for 24 hours yet.

290
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:38,940
I can tell from my brother-in-law

291
00:22:39,024 --> 00:22:41,109
that doctors lack a sense of unity.

292
00:22:42,778 --> 00:22:45,280
They're too full of themselves
to unify for one cause.

293
00:22:46,156 --> 00:22:49,451
I heard they are set to go on strike.
I've never seen them unify so quickly.

294
00:22:51,203 --> 00:22:52,454
It's not a good thing.

295
00:22:54,164 --> 00:22:57,125
-You're right, sir.
-The cargo union is still causing trouble.

296
00:22:57,209 --> 00:23:01,004
And yet, I reassigned you, who is
the most competent in dealing with unions,

297
00:23:01,088 --> 00:23:04,424
as the president of the hospital
because I would like you…

298
00:23:08,595 --> 00:23:09,846
to generate revenue

299
00:23:10,847 --> 00:23:12,224
that can sustain the entire group.

300
00:23:34,788 --> 00:23:38,375
Medical school, hospital,
insurance, and pharmaceuticals.

301
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:41,753
We finally have all four pillars
of the medical industry.

302
00:23:44,047 --> 00:23:46,091
Why do you think
I put you in that position?

303
00:23:47,717 --> 00:23:49,302
How many of our subsidiaries

304
00:23:49,386 --> 00:23:51,721
do you think will last
more than ten years?

305
00:23:52,264 --> 00:23:54,099
The medical industry
is a promising sector.

306
00:23:55,225 --> 00:23:57,686
In this era, hospitals are
where everyone eventually ends up.

307
00:23:57,769 --> 00:24:01,606
Companies spent decades instilling
the idea that medical care is a service.

308
00:24:02,107 --> 00:24:05,110
Do you think we built private hospitals,
added more beds,

309
00:24:05,193 --> 00:24:07,195
and invested for nothing?

310
00:24:08,363 --> 00:24:10,115
The market is finally ready.

311
00:24:10,949 --> 00:24:12,409
Now is the time we grow our business.

312
00:24:15,162 --> 00:24:18,707
People won't complain about the hospital
having problems after you took over.

313
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:20,041
I'll make sure of it.

314
00:24:20,834 --> 00:24:22,794
I trust your words.

315
00:24:24,296 --> 00:24:27,215
Regarding the construction
of the building in Songtan,

316
00:24:27,299 --> 00:24:28,800
the headquarters will fund it, correct?

317
00:24:31,553 --> 00:24:32,596
You can…

318
00:24:33,597 --> 00:24:34,681
trust my words.

319
00:24:36,892 --> 00:24:37,934
Not all of it though.

320
00:24:39,394 --> 00:24:40,437
Not all of it. I see.

321
00:24:41,646 --> 00:24:42,814
Thank you, Mr. Cho.

322
00:24:59,748 --> 00:25:01,249
…to generate revenue

323
00:25:02,334 --> 00:25:03,668
that can sustain the entire group.

324
00:25:10,383 --> 00:25:11,801
Mr. Gu is here.

325
00:25:14,346 --> 00:25:16,640
I'm Park Jong-sang from Hwajeong Chemical.

326
00:25:21,228 --> 00:25:22,812
I must have kept you waiting for so long.

327
00:25:23,563 --> 00:25:24,564
Please have a seat.

328
00:25:26,024 --> 00:25:26,942
Have a seat.

329
00:25:46,002 --> 00:25:47,545
Where should we begin?

330
00:25:48,672 --> 00:25:50,382
We would like to start with drug muggers.

331
00:25:50,924 --> 00:25:53,885
Long-term use of strong drugs
can lead to liver damage

332
00:25:53,969 --> 00:25:57,264
or nutritional deficiency
due to the drug-mugging effect.

333
00:25:57,347 --> 00:25:59,641
Since this is a general hospital,
we want to target that

334
00:25:59,724 --> 00:26:01,726
and help patients make up
for the deficient nutrients

335
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:02,852
with our supplements.

336
00:26:04,646 --> 00:26:06,856
The doctors could tell the patients

337
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:10,360
that their medication hinders
the absorption of certain nutrients

338
00:26:10,443 --> 00:26:12,904
and recommend our products.

339
00:26:14,114 --> 00:26:14,990
And this.

340
00:26:17,117 --> 00:26:20,161
If you put these up on the wall
or in the elevators,

341
00:26:20,245 --> 00:26:22,956
the patients will naturally
become aware of our products.

342
00:26:24,499 --> 00:26:26,126
And these are weight-loss supplements.

343
00:26:26,710 --> 00:26:27,877
These are the latest products.

344
00:26:27,961 --> 00:26:30,880
