-Who?

424
00:32:16,309 --> 00:32:17,685
The one who played the dead man.

425
00:32:18,353 --> 00:32:19,979
The one who posted
the financial statement.

426
00:32:20,730 --> 00:32:23,066
-What?
-Do you know Ye Jin-woo?

427
00:32:23,149 --> 00:32:24,901
The one in Emergency Medicine? It was him?

428
00:32:26,402 --> 00:32:29,781
Is that why he spoke up
during yesterday's meeting?

429
00:32:30,406 --> 00:32:32,659
-It's surprising.
-What is?

430
00:32:32,742 --> 00:32:35,870
He was the type who never speaks up.

431
00:32:37,580 --> 00:32:40,833
Is he one
of Chief Joo Kyung-moon's people?

432
00:32:40,917 --> 00:32:42,210
What? Why?

433
00:32:42,293 --> 00:32:44,128
Maybe they worked together.

434
00:32:46,589 --> 00:32:47,632
Well,

435
00:32:49,676 --> 00:32:51,803
It's not like Chief Joo is
a nobody from nowhere, but…

436
00:32:51,886 --> 00:32:54,597
Someone from Sangkook must have been
considered for his position.

437
00:32:55,223 --> 00:32:57,684
But the director hired him
instead of that candidate.

438
00:32:57,767 --> 00:32:59,394
I told you. He is an outcast.

439
00:33:00,436 --> 00:33:03,106
Chief Joo has no "people"
that he looks after or looks after him.

440
00:33:03,189 --> 00:33:05,024
Then who are those two close to?

441
00:33:05,525 --> 00:33:07,819
What are you scheming this time?

442
00:33:07,902 --> 00:33:09,988
You'll find out if you tell me.

443
00:33:10,071 --> 00:33:11,990
Ye Jin-woo's close to Dr. Lee No-eul.

444
00:33:12,073 --> 00:33:14,158
I think there's something going on
between them,

445
00:33:14,242 --> 00:33:15,410
but they act like there isn't.

446
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,996
Chief Joo likes everyone,

447
00:33:18,079 --> 00:33:19,664
but isn't close to anyone.

448
00:33:19,747 --> 00:33:22,917
You must be close to Jin-woo.
You even know about his woman.

449
00:33:23,543 --> 00:33:25,128
Not necessarily.

450
00:33:25,837 --> 00:33:28,339
What do you mean? Is Lee No-eul a man?

451
00:33:28,423 --> 00:33:29,674
And he and Ye Jin-woo…

452
00:33:29,757 --> 00:33:31,926
No. Lee No-eul is a woman.

453
00:33:33,553 --> 00:33:37,348
I don't know Dr. Ye very well.
