457
00:33:45,815 --> 00:33:47,316
So, something bad will happen?

458
00:33:52,280 --> 00:33:54,532
Forget it. It's all crap.

459
00:33:57,785 --> 00:33:58,911
Doctors and nurses alike.

460
00:34:12,258 --> 00:34:13,760
Do you want a different position?

461
00:34:14,927 --> 00:34:17,305
It's nice having a friend
as the new president.

462
00:34:21,184 --> 00:34:23,269
It's the same anywhere in the hospital.

463
00:34:24,228 --> 00:34:25,480
Why bother?

464
00:34:26,981 --> 00:34:28,483
Not within the hospital.

465
00:34:29,817 --> 00:34:31,069
How about the Restructure Team?

466
00:34:31,152 --> 00:34:33,237
They're already talking about
going on strike.

467
00:34:33,321 --> 00:34:35,198
Whether you restructure or whatever,

468
00:34:35,281 --> 00:34:36,741
you should've brought them in later.

469
00:34:37,658 --> 00:34:38,951
It is the best timing.

470
00:34:40,745 --> 00:34:42,747
This is the best timing?

471
00:34:42,830 --> 00:34:45,208
Restructuring during this mayhem?

472
00:34:47,293 --> 00:34:48,252
Yes.

