773
00:57:36,369 --> 00:57:38,288
That's right. The patients…

774
00:57:40,790 --> 00:57:42,459
Let's go on a partial strike.

775
00:57:43,209 --> 00:57:46,588
Let's have people rotate
between treating patients and protesting

776
00:57:47,088 --> 00:57:48,923
until we get the public on our side.

777
00:57:51,134 --> 00:57:53,470
-And if that doesn't work?
-We fight head-on.

778
00:57:55,221 --> 00:57:58,808
We have justification.
We'll show we aren't just whining.

779
00:57:59,434 --> 00:58:02,187
Chief Joo, put together a schedule
for when the staff members

780
00:58:02,270 --> 00:58:04,731
should treat patients or protest
starting tomorrow.

781
00:58:04,814 --> 00:58:06,065
Pardon?

782
00:58:06,149 --> 00:58:08,651
Alone? For every single department?

783
00:58:09,611 --> 00:58:13,948
He worries about the patients the most
in our entire hospital.

784
00:58:15,366 --> 00:58:16,826
I have faith

785
00:58:16,910 --> 00:58:19,787
that with that attitude, you can ensure
the patients won't be affected.

786
00:58:19,871 --> 00:58:23,208
How could I decide
other department's schedule--

787
00:58:23,291 --> 00:58:25,460
I'll have our list of staff
and schedules sent over

788
00:58:26,127 --> 00:58:29,964
since you're excellent
at getting things done.

789
00:58:30,048 --> 00:58:31,883
I'll send our department's schedules, too.

790
00:58:32,509 --> 00:58:34,511
Oh, right.
We can't take part in the strike.

791
00:58:35,011 --> 00:58:36,971
Okay, that settles it. Next…

792
00:58:37,514 --> 00:58:38,515
Hold on.

793
00:58:38,598 --> 00:58:41,768
I'm sure everyone has figured it out
within their departments.

794
00:58:41,851 --> 00:58:43,978
-What do you mean?
-Who posted the financial statement.

795
00:58:44,604 --> 00:58:46,731
The person who figured out
that the departments

796
00:58:46,814 --> 00:58:49,400
were being kicked out for creating
losses, not for support purposes.

797
00:58:50,109 --> 00:58:53,571
It was probably someone from one
of the three departments. Why?

798
00:58:53,655 --> 00:58:55,615
We should find out who it was

799
00:58:55,698 --> 00:58:57,784
and grill them to see what else they know.

800
00:58:58,409 --> 00:59:00,286
We should use everything we can.

801
00:59:00,370 --> 00:59:03,206
If that person knew more, I'm sure
there would've been more posts.

802
00:59:04,624 --> 00:59:05,833
You don't know, Dr. Kim?

803
00:59:07,085 --> 00:59:08,962
I don't think Mr. Gu knows, either.

804
00:59:09,045 --> 00:59:10,630
If he knew,

805
00:59:10,713 --> 00:59:12,715
he would've openly terminated
that person already.

806
00:59:17,011 --> 00:59:20,640
The chief of Pediatrics and I thought
it was someone from our department,

807
00:59:21,432 --> 00:59:24,060
but no one's talking about it.

808
00:59:29,232 --> 00:59:32,402
Doctors in my department
don't even have time to eat.

809
00:59:33,903 --> 00:59:35,738
If we find out,
everyone else will as well.

810
00:59:35,822 --> 00:59:37,323
It would only expose the person.

811
00:59:37,949 --> 00:59:39,450
No hospital will accept a doctor

812
00:59:39,534 --> 00:59:41,369
who blew the whistle on their hospital.

813
00:59:42,078 --> 00:59:44,539
That person kept us
from becoming helpless victims.

814
00:59:45,290 --> 00:59:47,208
We should protect that person.

815
00:59:51,754 --> 00:59:53,673
Everyone's drinking, right?

816
00:59:54,465 --> 00:59:56,926
I'm on call, so I need to go. Excuse me.

817
01:00:21,034 --> 01:00:24,037
I've never had a chief
do grunt work before.

818
01:00:24,871 --> 01:00:27,165
It's nice having someone
who isn't from the same university.

819
01:00:32,420 --> 01:00:33,796
Are you upset about this afternoon?

820
01:00:35,006 --> 01:00:39,052
I understand. Mr. Gu has something huge
holding over his head now.

821
01:00:40,386 --> 01:00:41,554
It's not just us.

822
01:00:41,638 --> 01:00:43,765
Is there anyone here
who has nothing to hide?

823
01:00:44,807 --> 01:00:45,683
There is.

824
01:00:46,517 --> 01:00:49,854
You shouldn't have done anything
that could be used against you.

825
01:00:51,189 --> 01:00:53,983
I wanted to applaud Mr. Gu on this one.

826
01:00:55,485 --> 01:00:57,445
What? No matter what happens,

827
01:00:57,528 --> 01:01:00,073
it always ends with internal reports
and confidential disciplines.

828
01:01:01,032 --> 01:01:02,867
If you didn't want an outsider
interfering,

829
01:01:02,950 --> 01:01:04,827
you shouldn't have given him ammo.

830
01:01:05,536 --> 01:01:07,705
Once he starts to interfere with
every little thing,

831
01:01:07,789 --> 01:01:09,832
our residents will suffer. That's why.

832
01:01:09,916 --> 01:01:13,503
Don't just talk about
how much the residents are suffering.

833
01:01:13,586 --> 01:01:15,088
Go to the hospital

834
01:01:15,171 --> 01:01:17,965
and yell at them like I do,
instead of going golfing.

835
01:01:21,636 --> 01:01:22,720
Are you leaving?

836
01:01:22,804 --> 01:01:25,765
Yes. I need to sleep early
and get up early to yell at them again.

837
01:01:26,307 --> 01:01:27,308
Goodbye.

838
01:01:32,271 --> 01:01:35,233
-She never gives in.
-Why should she?

839
01:01:35,983 --> 01:01:36,901
Sorry?

840
01:02:03,803 --> 01:02:05,638
He's so frustrating.

841
01:02:14,522 --> 01:02:15,523
Gosh.

842
01:02:16,441 --> 01:02:17,775
How could you leave like that…

843
01:02:19,110 --> 01:02:20,820
after bringing me here?

844
01:02:44,761 --> 01:02:45,595
You're leaving late.

845
01:02:46,345 --> 01:02:47,263
Yes.

846
01:02:47,346 --> 01:02:49,223
Good night. See you tomorrow.

847
01:03:39,982 --> 01:03:41,984
ANNOUNCEMENT
OF SANGKOOK UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL STRIKE

848
01:03:43,277 --> 01:03:45,112
WITHDRAW EXPULSION ORDER
ON THE 3 DEPARTMENTS

849
01:03:45,196 --> 01:03:47,240
WITHDRAW EXPULSION ORDER
ON THE 3 DEPARTMENTS

850
01:03:48,449 --> 01:03:49,450
"Announcement of strike.

851
01:03:51,118 --> 01:03:52,537
Sangkook University Hospital

852
01:03:53,120 --> 01:03:56,958
will go on strike to demand
that the expulsion order

853
01:03:57,041 --> 01:04:00,127
on Obstetrics and Gynecology, Pediatrics,
and Emergency Medicine

854
01:04:00,211 --> 01:04:03,506
be withdrawn, as per the vote result

855
01:04:03,589 --> 01:04:06,050
that showed over 80% of the staff
agree to go on strike.

856
01:04:08,845 --> 01:04:12,682
The expulsion of the three departments
is an insult to the medical staff

857
01:04:12,765 --> 01:04:16,018
who did their best for the patients

858
01:04:16,102 --> 01:04:19,230
even in poor working conditions.

859
01:04:19,313 --> 01:04:20,898
Our battle

860
01:04:20,982 --> 01:04:24,193
is to protect the patients' lives
and basic rights.

861
01:04:24,277 --> 01:04:27,697
Thus, we plead with everyone out there
desperately.

862
01:04:31,492 --> 01:04:32,994
If we cannot come to an agreement

863
01:04:33,077 --> 01:04:35,955
with the foundation
by the predetermined date,

864
01:04:36,998 --> 01:04:39,834
we will enter into a full-scale strike.

865
01:04:40,334 --> 01:04:42,378
Everyone will be striking then.

866
01:04:45,172 --> 01:04:49,927
The medical staff are not holding
patients hostage by striking.

867
01:04:50,720 --> 01:04:53,180
We simply seek to cease the misconduct
by the management,

868
01:04:53,264 --> 01:04:55,641
which is ignorant
of the reality of the medical field,

869
01:04:56,142 --> 01:04:59,854
and to point out what is wrong.
This is, unfortunately,

870
01:04:59,937 --> 01:05:01,606
a necessary recourse.

871
01:05:02,398 --> 01:05:04,984
Through a fair and just strike,
we will build

872
01:05:05,067 --> 01:05:07,320
the employees' faith in us

873
01:05:07,403 --> 01:05:12,199
as well as the faith everyone
who visits this hospital has in us.

874
01:05:12,825 --> 01:05:17,038
Regardless of the pressure
from the management, we will not give up,

875
01:05:17,121 --> 01:05:19,916
and we will defend
our reputation and status

876
01:05:19,999 --> 01:05:23,961
as the best private university hospital
in the nation."

877
01:05:40,645 --> 01:05:41,854
SURGERY DEPARTMENT
DUTY SCHEDULE

878
01:06:23,938 --> 01:06:25,690
Our end must be near,

879
01:06:25,773 --> 01:06:29,110
seeing what Mr. Gu is doing
even with our threat of striking.

880
01:06:29,193 --> 01:06:30,903
He isn't wrong.

881
01:06:30,987 --> 01:06:32,154
It's all true.

882
01:06:32,238 --> 01:06:34,991
You need to put an end to it
before he starts officially.

883
01:06:35,074 --> 01:06:38,536
The cargo union is super tough,
but he destroyed them.

884
01:06:38,619 --> 01:06:39,912
That young kid did.

885
01:06:39,996 --> 01:06:41,580
He opened a can of worms.

886
01:06:41,664 --> 01:06:44,709
Sangkook University Hospital
is fourth in revenue.

887
01:06:44,792 --> 01:06:47,169
It means that it can lose its place
in a second.

888
01:06:47,878 --> 01:06:49,714
Everyone makes money the same way.

889
01:06:49,797 --> 01:06:52,383
Was the report
about the death at the Cancer Center

890
01:06:52,466 --> 01:06:54,719
fabricated by the management as well?

891
01:06:54,802 --> 01:06:58,014
You can't criticize the management
entirely, then.

892
01:06:58,097 --> 01:07:01,350
How bad must it be for you people
to announce it publicly?

893
01:07:01,434 --> 01:07:03,894
You'd never announce it
before it somehow gets out, right?

894
01:07:03,978 --> 01:07:06,647
What if I didn't check
and ended up giving him double doses?

895
01:07:08,899 --> 01:07:09,734
I'm sorry.

896
01:07:09,817 --> 01:07:11,986
Do you think it is okay
because it doesn't kill?

897
01:07:12,069 --> 01:07:15,614
We're no better than the Cancer Center.
We've just been lucky.

898
01:07:15,698 --> 01:07:19,243
Anyone at a chief level
can be a candidate for the director.

899
01:07:19,326 --> 01:07:20,953
Why don't you register as a candidate?

900
